XrmOptionDescRec {.final, pure.} = object
  option*: cstring           ## Option abbreviation in argv.
  specifier*: cstring        ## Resource specifier.
  arg_kind*: XrmOptionKind   ## Which style of option it is.
  value*: XPointer           ## Value to provide if XrmoptionNoArg.
  
XrmOptionKind {.size: 4.} = enum
  XrmoptionNoArg,           ## Value is specified in OptionDescRec.value.
  XrmoptionIsArg,           ## Value is the option string itself.
  XrmoptionStickyArg,       ## Value is characters immediately following option.
  XrmoptionSepArg,          ## Value is next argument in argv.
  XrmoptionResArg,          ## Resource and value in next argument in argv.
  XrmoptionSkipArg,         ## Ignore this option and the next argument in argv.
  XrmoptionSkipLine,        ## Ignore this option and the rest of argv.
  XrmoptionSkipNArgs         ## Ignore this option and the next
                             ## OptionDescRes.value arguments in argv.
